abstract: Rupert Murdoch and family spend some quality time in front of the camera for Britain’s Hello magazine.
snippet: Rupert Murdoch and family spend some quality time in front of the camera for Britain’s Hello magazine.
lead_paragraph: As a newspaperman with an ear for his audience, Rupert Murdoch, the chief executive of the News Corporation, has long expressed his distaste for elites and royals. But plenty of both were in attendance recently as Mr. Murdoch and his wife Wendi celebrated the christening of their two daughters, Grace and Chloe.

headline.main: Rupert Murdoch and Family Find Faith and Fame at the River Jordan

abstract: Income rose more than 37 percent as Google’s online advertising business continued to hum along nicely.
snippet: Income rose more than 37 percent as Google’s online advertising business continued to hum along nicely.
lead_paragraph: SAN FRANCISCO — Google may be fighting a multifront war against Apple, Microsoft, federal antitrust regulators and the government of China, but its online advertising business continues to hum along nicely.

headline.main: Google’s Profit and Revenue Rise, but Analysts Wanted More
headline.print_headline: Google’s Profit Rises 37% and Its Revenue 23%, but Analysts Wanted More
